tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE at_risk_population (
	health_record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	patient_id INT,
	demographic_id INT,
	disease_id INT,
	age INT,
	gender TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name TEXT,
  last_name TEXT,
  date_of_birth DATE,
  gender TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE HealthRecords (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT REFERENCES Patients(patient_id),
  diagnosis TEXT,
  treatment TEXT,
  record_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE health_records (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  disease VARCHAR(50),
  diagnosis_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE demographic_information (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  location VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE at_risk_population (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  risk_score INT,
  risk_factor VARCHAR(50),
  risk_level VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE HealthRecords (
    record_id UUID,
    patient_id UUID,
    disease_id UUID,
    diagnosis_date DATE,
    PRIMARY KEY (record_id)
);

CREATE TABLE DemographicInformation (
    patient_id UUID,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
    PRIMARY KEY (patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE AtRiskPopulations (
    risk_id UUID,
    patient_id UUID,
    risk_factor VARCHAR(50),
    risk_score INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (risk_id)
);
